title: Leick Mission Console Table/Hall Stand, Russet
description: Do you have a narrow hallway or landing that needs that special something? The attractive Leick Mission Console Table/Hall Stand is a perfect solution for this small space. A narrow 10 inch footprint allows this table to fit in tight spaces and brings beauty and functionality to your home. A rich hand applied multi-step Russet finish accentuates the natural beauty of the wood grain and solid wood construction ensures many years of enjoyment. The wide table top, storage drawer and lower display shelf offers a home to entryway storage, your favorite lamp and decor item.
